    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Slice your <strong>sweet pointed pepper[s]</strong> into rings</p><p>Once the chicken is starting to brown, add the <strong>onion wedges</strong> and <strong>sliced pepper</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1684913018958-x200.jpg",
