      "instruction": "<p>To serve, drizzle the <strong>roasted garlic aioli </strong>over the <strong>one-pot chicken paella</strong></p><p>To garnish, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> roughly over the paella with scissors</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
